text: Rudolf Kloeckner (born 10 June 1917) was a Romanian alpine skier. He competed in the men's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1917 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Romanian male alpine skiers Category:Romanian male cross-country skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Romania Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Romania Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
